        <Summary>General purpose parser generator</Summary>
        <Description>Bison is a general-purpose parser generator that converts an annotated context-free grammar into a deterministic LR or generalized LR (GLR) parser employing LALR(1) parser tables. As an experimental feature, Bison can also generate IELR(1) or canonical LR(1) parser tables. It is upward compatible with Yacc</Description>
